latestPosts.caption:
6 years ago this space was created! 
Boojee was founded here (now Boojee A but just Boojee back then) sorry for too much boojee 

Over the years it wore down and needed some love,attention and makeover (how sometimes we do) 

just how we like to change, recreate, evolve with our menu, sometimes we need the same with our cafe too! 
So we have recreated this space for making it a 16 seater upgraded version of Boojee, for more memories, more conversations 🤍
a warm small space for a quick coffee, matcha or breakfast for you! 

Come find your favourite table 👋
